name: Funkot
description: Fast-paced Indonesian form of Electronic Dance Music that combines Eurodance and Trance synths with the syncopated rhythm from Dangdut koplo.

children.name: Breakbeat Kota
children.description: Indonesian style that slows down the syncopated rhythms of Funkot to moderate tempos around 130 BPM.
